              <additions>
                <list>
                  <item n="2" xml:id="addition2">
                    <p>Both Greek (<!-- Missing Greek vowels --> ) and Syriac vowels have been added by later hands, and the points rukkākh and kushshāi occur on foll. <locus from="3b" to="6b">3 b— 6 b</locus>.</p>
                  </item>
                  <item n="3" xml:id="addition3">
                    <p>Other lessons have been added by later hands.</p>
                  </item>
                  <item n="4" xml:id="addition4">
                    <locus from="106a" to="106a"/>
                    <p>The note which originally stood on fol. 106 a, after the doxology, has been erased, and another substituted for it, stating that this manuscript and four others were presented to <placeName ref="">the convent of S. Mary Deipara</placeName> by a monk named <persName ref="">John</persName>. </p>
                    <p><quote xml:lang="syr">ܝܗ̣ܒ ܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ ܕܦܪܟܣܝܣ ܘܐܪ̈ܒܥܐ ܐܚܪ̈ܢܐ ܠܕܝܪܐ ܕܝܠܕܬ ܐܠܗܐ ܕܣܘܪ̈ܝܝܐ̣. ܝܘܚܢܢ ܐܚܐ ܢܟܦܐ ܘܕܝܪܝܐ. ܘܠܐ ܫܠܝܛ ܠܐܢܫ ܡܢ ܐܠܗܐ ܕܢ̇ܦܩ ܐܢܘܢ ܡܢܗ̇ ܕܕܝܪܐ ܒܙܢܐ ܐܝܢܐ ܕܗ̣ܘ ܟܡܐ ܕܐܝܬ ܒܕܝܪܐ ܕܝܪ̈ܝܐ. ܗ̇ܘ ܕܝܢ ܕܣܥ̇ܐ ܥܠ ܗܕܐ܆ ܢܚܝܒܝܘܗܝ ܡܪܝܐ ܒܝܘܡ ܕܝܢ̣ܐ ܘܢܣܝܡ ܡܢ̇ܬܗ ܥܡ ܡ̈ܚܠܨܝ ܒܝܬ ܡܩܕܫܐ܀ ܠܝܘܚܢܢ ܕܝܢ ܕܫ̇ܟܢ ܐܢܘܢ ܠܟ̈ܬܒܐ ܗܠܝܢ ܠܕܝܪܐ܆ ܡܪܝܐ ܢܚܣܐ ܠܗ ܒܝܕ ܨ̈ܠܘܬܐ ܕܟܠܗ̇ ܥܕܬܐ ܐܡܝܢ ܐܡܝܢ♰</quote></p>
                    <!-- Shape of the cross is different than here -->
                  </item>
                  <item n="5" xml:id="addition5">
                    <locus from="106a" to="106a"/>
                    <p><quote xml:lang="syr">ܘܟܠ ܕܢܠܚܐ ܥܘܗܕܢܐ ܗܢܐ ܘܟܐܡ ܥܠ܏ܘ ܡܚܪܡܐ ܢܗܘܐ ܐܡܝܢ.</quote></p>
                  </item>
                  <item n="6" xml:id="addition6">
                    <locus from="108a" to="108a"/>
                    <p>At the foot of fol. 108 a is written the name of one <listPerson><person ref=""><persName>Joseph, </persName><persName xml:lang="syr">ܝܘܣܦ</persName></person></listPerson>.</p>
                  </item>
                </list>
